---
title: Lemony Broccoli & Pork Sausage Soup with Carrots & Couscous
description: This one-pot soup stars hearty pork sausage simmered in a garlicky broth with a colorful cast of broccoli, carrots, and bouncy pearl couscous. Add a touch of silkiness with a swirl of crème fraîche and finish with a bright squeeze of lemon juice for tangy flavor and luscious texture that beckons to your very favorite bowls.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66019b8ada283ecbc2883d4e-b10b5aae.jpeg
